  "body": "<!--\r\nNeed help?\r\nRefer to our contributing guidelines for additional information about making a good issue:\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum-optimism/.github/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md\r\n-->\r\n\r\n**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nTo enable (and test) self-withdrawals, we'll need the ability for anyone to relay a withdrawal, this means removing the `onlyRelayer` modifier on `relayMessage`\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\nJust delete the modifier `onlyRelayer` https://github.com/ethereum-optimism/optimism/blob/536e02b54b34608045f9d476d3956062671f687b/packages/contracts/contracts/optimistic-ethereum/OVM/bridge/messaging/OVM_L1CrossDomainMessenger.sol#L81-L90\r\nand remove instances of setting the `OVM_L2MessageRelayer` in the AddressManager\r\n",
